languages.text: "Не стоит, Ваша Светлость. Вы не сможете, а я — не хочу. Если вы не поняли, существование в этом теле куда хуже и страшнее, чем пытки, которым меня подвергали прежде. Хорошо, что оно заканчивается".

traits.locale_text: "Не стоит, Ваша Светлость. Вы не сможете, а я — не хочу. Если вы не поняли, существование в этом теле куда хуже и страшнее, чем пытки, которым меня подвергали прежде. Хорошо, что оно заканчивается".
traits.speaker: WrackServant

languages.text: "Spare yourself the effort, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. You will not be able to and it is not something I want. In case you did not understand, the existence in this body is far worse than the torment they subjected me to. I am glad it is about to end."

languages.text: 「努力することなどありませんよ、陛下。あなたにはできないし、私が望んでいることでもない。あなたは理解していないかもしれないが、この肉体での存在は、彼らが私を苦しめたことよりも遥かにひどいものです。それが終わろうとしていることを嬉しく思います」
languages.original_text: "Spare yourself the effort, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. You will not be able to and it is not something I want. In case you did not understand, the existence in this body is far worse than the torment they subjected me to. I am glad it is about to end."

traits.speaker: WrackServant

languages.text: “别白费力气了，大人。您恐怕救不了我，我也不想再活下去了。或许您不太明白，光是在这个身体里活着，就比他们对我的那些折磨还要痛苦得多。我很高兴，这一切终于要结束了。”
languages.original_text: "Spare yourself the effort, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. You will not be able to and it is not something I want. In case you did not understand, the existence in this body is far worse than the torment they subjected me to. I am glad it is about to end."

traits.speaker: WrackServant

languages.text: «Ahórrese el esfuerzo, mi{mf|lord|lady}. No podrá hacerlo y, de todas formas, no es lo que deseo. Por si no lo ha entendido, vivir con este cuerpo es mucho peor que el tormento al que me habían sometido. Me alegro de que esté a punto de terminar».
languages.original_text: "Spare yourself the effort, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. You will not be able to and it is not something I want. In case you did not understand, the existence in this body is far worse than the torment they subjected me to. I am glad it is about to end."

traits.speaker: WrackServant

languages.text: "Spart Euch die Mühe, Euer {mf|Lordschaft|Ladyschaft}. Das könntet Ihr nicht, und ich will es auch nicht. Falls Ihr es noch nicht begriffen habt, die Existenz in diesem Körper ist sehr viel schlimmer als die Qualen, die sie mich haben erleiden lassen. Ich bin froh, dass sie bald enden wird."
languages.original_text: "Spare yourself the effort, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. You will not be able to and it is not something I want. In case you did not understand, the existence in this body is far worse than the torment they subjected me to. I am glad it is about to end."

languages.text: « Inutile de vous donner cette peine, Votre Seigneurie. Vous n'en seriez pas capable, et ce n'est pas ce que je souhaite de toute façon. Au cas où vous ne l'auriez pas encore compris, vivre dans ce corps est un tourment bien plus grand que toutes les tortures qu'ils m'ont fait subir. Il est temps d'en finir, et personne n'en serait plus heureux que moi. »
languages.original_text: "Spare yourself the effort, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. You will not be able to and it is not something I want. In case you did not understand, the existence in this body is far worse than the torment they subjected me to. I am glad it is about to end."

languages.text: "Boşuna uğraşmayın {mf|Lord|Leydi} Hazretleri. Beni kurtaramazsınız, kaldı ki kurtarmanızı istemem. Farkında mısınız bilmem ama bu bedende var olmak, bana çektirdikleri işkenceden katbekat kötü. Sona erecek olmasından memnunum."
languages.original_text: "Spare yourself the effort, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. You will not be able to and it is not something I want. In case you did not understand, the existence in this body is far worse than the torment they subjected me to. I am glad it is about to end."

traits.locale_text: "Boşuna uğraşmayın {mf|Lord|Leydi} Hazretleri. Beni kurtaramazsınız ve istediğim de bu değil. Eğer farkında değilseniz bu bedende var olmak, beni maruz bıraktıkları işkenceden katbekat kötü. Sona erecek olmasından memnunum."
traits.speaker: WrackServant
